    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/1df6317fe271196c72c664a16c58e988.avif?t=1756036493\" width=800 height=34 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过免费试玩版，体验 GUG 的魅力。输入任意词语或短语，看着一个生物诞生，并让它与敌方 gug 战斗。这很短暂、荒诞，但超级有趣……<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/b61259797ec40160d88559f76e0bfd70.poster.avif?t=1756036493\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/b61259797ec40160d88559f76e0bfd70.webm?t=1756036493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/b61259797ec40160d88559f76e0bfd70.mp4?t=1756036493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/cc4e755065b680dbaeaa6230f2a9b743.avif?t=1756036493\" width=800 height=34 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的基于输入文字的生物生成系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个循环进行的类 roguelike 战斗遭遇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于程序逻辑的能力、属性及行为</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精选环境变体与取胜条件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >初现端倪的“造物神情结”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/4e97356d9819ff9187bf8a2a0f4ec785.poster.avif?t=1756036493\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/4e97356d9819ff9187bf8a2a0f4ec785.webm?t=1756036493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/4e97356d9819ff9187bf8a2a0f4ec785.mp4?t=1756036493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/b1f2d909c07b13f7e1a60f7a66f0bc7b.avif?t=1756036493\" width=800 height=34 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使是试玩版，也不会有两个一模一样的 gug。输入“逃税巫师”或“潮湿的黄瓜噩梦”，看看会出现什么奇怪的怪物——然后再试一次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/8f92e29aa30be14cc8a4d6dd8f0cd784.poster.avif?t=1756036493\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/8f92e29aa30be14cc8a4d6dd8f0cd784.webm?t=1756036493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/8f92e29aa30be14cc8a4d6dd8f0cd784.mp4?t=1756036493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 GUG 疯狂的沙盒模拟中，体验独一无二的怪异，无需任何压力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256600/extras/53fffdeb2f9a01c6cccacdb639853c2a.avif?t=1756036493\" width=800 height=53 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你半夜 1 点打字输入“量子汤宝宝”只为了看看会发生什么，建议你将完整版加入愿望清单。后续还有很多内容，也许多到超乎想象？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
